Depends:
 python3-httpx,
 ${misc:Depends},
 ${python3:Depends},
Description: consume Server-Sent Events (SSE) with httpx (Avalan PPA transitive)
 httpx-sse is a small pure-Python helper that consumes Server-Sent
 Event streams over an httpx response, exposing them as an iterable of
 ``ServerSentEvent`` records. This package is built for the Avalan PPA
 because mcp (Avalan's `server` extras) requires `httpx-sse >= 0.4`
 and Noble does not ship the distribution. Pinned at 0.4.3, the
 latest release in the 0.4.x line.
 .
 Upstream's pyproject.toml declares no install_requires even though
 every public entry point imports httpx; python3-httpx is declared
 here explicitly so apt resolves it transitively.
